{"tid":1562424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"即日起 郭台銘退出中國國民黨","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T04:05:34.000Z","uid":116471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4694b5cc17287a2caad5f742ad4122633494730","tid":1562424,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"國民黨今（12日）於各報刊登有黨內31名大老親筆連署的廣告文，呼籲郭台銘與國民黨總統候選人韓國瑜合作後。郭台銘陣營、永齡基金會副執行長蔡沁瑜今（12日）出面回應時，聲明稱，郭台銘今宣布退出國民黨，預計今天下午會再發表正式聲明。"},{"pid":"612f1a84753add0b9b090042d1758375ba8bb885","tid":1562424,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}